                (a word or formula believed to have magic power)


Cast by WILD BASHKORT MAGES as part of the ICFP Programming Contest 2015.

... with love, from Bashkortostan, best country in the world.
    (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bashkortostan)


  Akhmetzyanov D. (linesprower@gmail.com)
    Head of Ufa State Automation Technical University.
      Credit: programming, eating, and sleeping; also, programming.

  Mouratov M. (mmouratov@gmail.com)
    Deputy of Bashkortostan Ministry of Love.
      Credit: direction, choreography, friendship, and magic.

  Ripatti A. (ripatti@inbox.ru)
    Yes, it's him. Representing Bashkortostan Opera House.
      Credit: baritone, beard, wisdom, and the lost art of video encoding.


  For the soundtrack, we have shamefully borrowed fragments of:
    1) Richard Strauss -- Also Sprach Zarathustra, Op. 30, performed by some
       awesome orchestra (we don't know exactly -- found it on youtube).

    2) A certain national anthem from "Borat". Hi, Borat, if you read this!


