   (a sacred ceremony in which the actions follow a prescribed order and form)


Conducted by WILD BASHKORT MAGES at the ICFP Contest 2015 Award Ceremony.

The enchanted digital artifact you now possess is meant to be activated on
the supported platforms in order to reproduce a realistic simulation of the
enriched and augmented version of THE RITUAL, given that basic support for
OpenGL is present (any modern PC should be fine).

All of the library dependencies are already included in the distribution.
Just run "bashkortostan" and let us know if something goes wrong.

Press SPACE to pause the demo, ESC to quit.

The "-windowed" command line switch (with "-width [int]" and "-height [int]",
optionally) can be used to constrain our magic to windowed mode, although
we strongly advise against it. One more available command is "-novsync".


